  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Consultant",
  "description": "<h1><strong>Sales Consultant (Maid Agency)</strong></h1>\n<p><br></p>\n<h3><strong>About Us</strong></h3>\n<p>Able Best Maid Agency has been trusted by Singapore families since 2003. For over 20 years, we’ve helped thousands of families find the right domestic helpers while supporting our helpers through training and guidance. We’re now looking for a <strong>responsible, motivated Sales Consultant</strong> who enjoys helping people, can communicate well, and is ready to grow with us.</p>\n<h3><strong>Why Join Us</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Stable job in a long-established company</strong> — we’ve been around since 2003.</li>\n  <li><strong>Structured training</strong> provided — learn how to match customers and helpers confidently.</li>\n  <li><strong>Friendly, family-style team</strong> that supports each other.</li>\n  <li><strong>Good earnings potential</strong> — steady basic pay + attractive commissions.</li>\n  <li><strong>Meaningful work</strong> — you’re helping families solve real problems every day.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Attend to customer enquiries (walk-ins, WhatsApp, phone calls).</li>\n  <li>Understand what each employer needs and recommend suitable helpers.</li>\n  <li>Arrange and guide interviews between employers and helpers.</li>\n  <li>Handle paperwork and follow-up after confirmation.</li>\n  <li>Keep communication clear and professional at every stage.</li>\n  <li>Work towards monthly targets with guidance from your manager.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Who We’re Looking For</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Pleasant, patient, and enjoys talking to people.</li>\n  <li>Responsible and able to follow up well with customers.</li>\n  <li>Can work independently once trained.</li>\n  <li>Comfortable using WhatsApp, email, and basic computer tools.</li>\n  <li>Prior sales or customer service experience an advantage, but not required — training provided.</li>\n  <li>Must be able to speak English; other languages (Mandarin, Bahasa, Tagalog, Burmese) a bonus.</li>\n  <li>CEI Certification is a plus </li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>What You’ll Get</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Basic Salary:</strong> $2,200 – $2,800 (depending on experience).</li>\n  <li><strong>Commission per placement</strong> — hard work rewarded fairly.</li>\n  <li><strong>Structured training and guidance</strong> from experienced teammates.</li>\n  <li>5.5 day week (Alternate week off days)</li>\n  <li>Long-term job stability in a reputable, well-established agency.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Apply directly through this portal.</strong><br>\nWe welcome both experienced consultants and those keen to learn and build a long-term career in this line.</p>",
